snippet.title: Outlaw 97 gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Outlaw 97, Dos PC game produced by Sandbird Software in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/outlaw-97/4533/
Outlaw 97 is an interesting action game, created in 1994. It is a fighting game multiplayer, first of three rounds wins.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
